00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:19,820
You don't know how it works.

404
00:39:20,380 --> 00:39:23,619
You shouldn't be. I mean, I'm giving you an extreme.

405
00:39:24,239 --> 00:39:27,860
Because that gun will not work unless it is in accordance with God's will.

406
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:32,559
And if it is God's will to die at that moment, there is nothing anyone in the whole world can do about it.

407
00:39:32,739 --> 00:39:35,719
Because the method and time of your death is already written down.

408
00:39:37,559 --> 00:39:41,920
And you cannot die except with a personal decree from God. Personal decree.

409
00:39:43,099 --> 00:39:48,579
It is a written decree. God must sign your death certificate.

410
00:39:49,719 --> 00:39:53,519
Therefore, a person comes with a gun, can do nothing to you.

411
00:39:54,699 --> 00:39:58,519
Because they have to have a signed certificate of your death from God, personally.

412
00:39:59,639 --> 00:40:03,579
No one knows when you will die, no one. This is what the Quran says, the end of Sura 31.

413
00:40:04,079 --> 00:40:05,639
Not even the angels know God's laws.

414
00:40:05,980 --> 00:40:07,880
The authority comes from Allah.

415
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:08,280
SubhanAllah.

416
00:40:09,619 --> 00:40:10,659
You had a question?

417
00:40:11,039 --> 00:40:12,940
Yeah, you said earlier that

418
00:40:13,579 --> 00:40:15,619
they would receive a double reward

419
00:40:15,619 --> 00:40:17,260
if they were to convert to

420
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:19,079
Submission. And

421
00:40:19,880 --> 00:40:21,420
it's stated before that

422
00:40:21,420 --> 00:40:22,800
everybody has to stay in caste.

423
00:40:23,720 --> 00:40:25,380
So I don't know

424
00:40:25,380 --> 00:40:27,099
if there's any kind of contradiction

425
00:40:27,099 --> 00:40:28,880
for them to get a double reward

426
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:30,659
if they're facing the same caste hurdles.

427
00:40:30,980 --> 00:40:33,280
No, they have additional hurdles

428
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:34,820
that they have to move across.

429
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:39,360
Because their clerics told them Jesus is God, he's the son of God, the trinity, this kind of thing.

430
00:40:39,559 --> 00:40:41,139
And they had to overcome this.

431
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:45,860
Besides, if God wants to be generous with them, there's nothing anyone can do.

432
00:40:46,059 --> 00:40:51,420
And God says that if you grow up under difficult circumstances and you come to the Quran,

433
00:40:52,539 --> 00:40:54,880
you will, you will receive double the reward.

434
00:40:55,039 --> 00:40:56,239
So that's more guidance.

435
00:40:57,320 --> 00:40:58,599
Yeah, that's more guidance.

436
00:40:59,199 --> 00:41:00,699
But it doesn't mean anything.

437
00:41:01,199 --> 00:41:01,940
Maybe it doesn't.

438
00:41:02,039 --> 00:41:02,480
Maybe not.

439
