The end, for example, the end of Surah Al-Baqarah, and they all quote the end of Surah Al-Baqarah.

440
00:41:13,739 --> 00:41:15,340
I will give a quote on that topic.

441
00:41:15,599 --> 00:41:15,840
That's all.

